md:
giải nghĩa từ "faster" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

### Faster

* Adverb: nhanh hơn, nhanh hơn nữa
* Meaning: (used to compare two things) more quickly or at a greater speed than something else.

Example sentence: "I can run faster than you."

* Related words: fast, quickly, rapid, swift, speed.

### Faster (in computing)

* Adjective: mạnh hơn, nhanh hơn
* Meaning: (of a computer or processor) able to perform operations more quickly.

Example sentence: "The new processor is faster and more efficient."

* Related words: fast, quick, rapid, swift, speed.

### Faster (in music)

* Adverb: nhanh hơn, nhanh hơn nữa
* Meaning: (of a musical tempo) at a quicker rate.

Example sentence: "The conductor asked the orchestra to play the piece faster."

* Related words: fast, quickly, rapid, swift, speed.

### Faster (in general)

* Adverb: nhanh hơn, nhanh hơn nữa
* Meaning: more quickly or at a greater rate than usual.

Example sentence: "We need to work faster to meet the deadline."

* Related words: fast, quickly, rapid, swift, speed.

Note: The meaning of "faster" can vary depending on the context in which it is used. The above explanations are some of the most common meanings of the word.
